    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3961870>
    dc:description "Fig. 18. Localities of Plagigeyeria species in Hercegovina and adjacent regions and the most likely distribution range of the known species within the related aquifers (colour blotches) and sampling localities (dots with numbers). Freshwater springs are in circles and brackish or submarine springs are as marked by diamonds, arrows show main karst conduits and locality numbers are according to the legend from Fig. 1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3961870/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

